<div class="content">
    <h1> Pro Tip</h1>
    <div id="pro-tip" style="background-color: #f1f1f1;">
        <br>
        Search a man page <br>
        with forward-slash:
        <div class="code" style="text-align: center; padding-left: 0">
            /&lt;search-term&gt;
        </div>
        Jump to the next match with
        <div class="code" style="text-align: center; padding-left: 0">
            n
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
